### HKG Flight Viewer - Worker API Examples
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = https://hkg-flight-proxy.lincoln995623.workers.dev

### ============================================================
### Live Data APIs
### ============================================================

### Get today's flights (all categories combined)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/flights

### Get airline information (check-in counters, names, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/airlines

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### ============================================================
### History APIs (D1 Database)
### ============================================================

### Get flight history (supports fuzzy match: CX888 â†’ CX 888)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history/flight/CX888

### Get flight history with space
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history/flight/CX 888

### Get cargo flight history (alphanumeric IATA: K4, 3S, 7L)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history/flight/5X055

### Get gate departure history
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history/gate/23

### Get all flights for a specific date
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/history/date/2026-01-15

### ============================================================
### Search & Autocomplete APIs
### ============================================================

### Get unique flight numbers (for autocomplete)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/flight-list

### Search flights by query
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?q=CX

### Search flights by airline
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?airline=CPA

### Search flights by date
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?date=2026-01-15

### ============================================================
### Statistics
### ============================================================

### Get D1 database statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/stats
